Package: libfinance-quote-grab-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: perl (>= 5.005), libfinance-quote-perl (>= 1.15), libhtml-tableextract-perl, libwww-perl (>= 5.814), libhttp-message-perl | libwww-perl, liburi-perl, libscalar-list-utils-perl | perl (>= 5.8), ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Download stock quotes from more places
 Finance-Quote-Grab extends Finance::Quote to download quotes from the
 following sources
  * MLC Funds
  * Reserve Bank of Australia (RBA)
  * Minneapolis Grain Exchange (MGEX)
